# supportedInteractions

**Instance Property**

The types of interactions that the configuration supports.

## Declaration

```swift
@MainActor var supportedInteractions: [UIActivityItemsConfigurationInteraction] { get set }
```

## Discussion

The default value is all known interactions.

## Managing supported interactions

- **UIActivityItemsConfigurationInteraction**: A structure that describes types of interactions.
